rows.label: qst202901_0010
rows.name: Wait!

rows.label: qst202901_0020
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Hmm?

rows.label: qst202901_0030
rows.name: You talking to us?

rows.label: qst202901_0040
rows.name: I wanted to talk to the pretty lady...

rows.label: qst202901_0050
rows.name: Oh, it's Tsuki you're after.

rows.label: qst202901_0060
rows.name: What's up, hon? You wanna ask me somethin'?

rows.label: qst202901_0070
rows.name: Um, can I...touch you?

rows.label: qst202901_0080
rows.name: Touch me? Well, sure, if you like...

rows.label: qst202901_0090
rows.name: Wow...so shiny! It's beautiful!

rows.label: qst202901_0100
rows.name: I wish I could wear something like this!

rows.label: qst202901_0110
rows.name: Thanks, hon.

rows.label: qst202901_0120
rows.name: And the way you talk is, is so lovely, too!

rows.label: qst202901_0130
rows.name:
It sounds so much more refined than
that guy over there!

rows.label: qst202901_0140
rows.name: Hey, why're you bringing me into this?!

rows.label: qst202901_0150
rows.name:
Well, that is mighty kind of you.
You're pretty cute yourself.

rows.label: qst202901_0160
rows.name: Hey, are you, like, a rabbit lady?!

rows.label: qst202901_0170
rows.name: Not quite, peaches. I'm a Blade, see?

rows.label: qst202901_0180
rows.name: Oh wow, a Blade! That's amazing!

rows.label: qst202901_0190
rows.name:
Name's Tsuki.
Pleasure to meet you.

rows.label: qst202901_0200
rows.name: Tsuki?

rows.label: qst202901_0210
rows.name: That's the one. Don't forget it, okay?

rows.label: qst202901_0220
rows.name: Okay!

rows.label: qst202901_0230
rows.name: So...hey, Tsuki!

rows.label: qst202901_0240
rows.name:
Why d'you look like that?
All shiny and pretty?

rows.label: qst202901_0250
rows.name:
Why? I'm not sure I can give you
a clean-cut answer there.

rows.label: qst202901_0260
rows.name: Are all Blades shiny and sparkly?!

rows.label: qst202901_0270
rows.name: Well, no, I suppose not.

rows.label: qst202901_0280
rows.name: Hey, Tsuki! Where'd you learn to talk like that?

rows.label: qst202901_0290
rows.name: It sounds way cooler than that guy over there!

rows.label: qst202901_0300
rows.name: Hey, can you please stop taking digs at me?!

rows.label: qst202901_0310
rows.name: I've talked like this all my life.

rows.label: qst202901_0320
rows.name: Hey hey, Tsuki!

rows.label: qst202901_0330
rows.name:
How'd you get to be born so beautiful?
And where'd you buy those shiny clothes?

rows.label: qst202901_0340
rows.name: Now, hold your horses!

rows.label: qst202901_0350
rows.name: One question at a time, if you please?

rows.label: qst202901_0360
rows.name: That kid really seems to have taken a shine to her.

rows.label: qst202901_0370
rows.name: Hey "pretty lady"! Keep it up!

rows.label: qst202901_0380
rows.name:
Ooh, they make me so mad sometimes...
Y'all are treadin' on thin ice!

rows.label: qst202901_0390
rows.name:
Hey, Tsuki! What's your favoritest
thing in the whole world?

rows.label: qst202901_0400
rows.name: My "favoritest" thing?

rows.label: qst202901_0410
rows.name: Yeah!

rows.label: qst202901_0420
rows.name: Well, let's see now...

rows.label: qst202901_0430
rows.name: I am pretty crazy about flowers.

rows.label: qst202901_0440
rows.name: Flowers?

rows.label: qst202901_0450
rows.name:
Uh-huh. There's these flowers that only
bloom at night - they're called Moondrops.

rows.label: qst202901_0460
rows.name:
Tiny li'l things, but they've got
beautiful white blossoms.

rows.label: qst202901_0470
rows.name: Huh...

rows.label: qst202901_0480
rows.name: Hey hey hey, Tsuki!

rows.label: qst202901_0490
rows.name: Listen, I wanna grow up to be just like you!

rows.label: qst202901_0500
rows.name: How can I be like you?

rows.label: qst202901_0510
rows.name: Be like me?

rows.label: qst202901_0520
rows.name: Uh-huh!

rows.label: qst202901_0530
rows.name: Hmmm... Well, I'm not sure 'bout that.

rows.label: qst202901_0540
rows.name: Maybe you should try playin' around outside.

rows.label: qst202901_0550
rows.name: Outside?

rows.label: qst202901_0560
rows.name:
That's right, hon. You've gotta
play hard, and eat well...

rows.label: qst202901_0570
rows.name:
Oh, and a little studying
wouldn't hurt either.

rows.label: qst202901_0580
rows.name: Whaaaa?! I've got to study?

rows.label: qst202901_0590
rows.name: Yup. Studying's pretty important, ya know.

rows.label: qst202901_0600
rows.name:
Wow... Being really pretty takes
a lot of work, huh.

rows.label: qst202901_0610
rows.name:
Whaddaya say, kid?
Got what you wanted?

rows.label: qst202901_0620
rows.name: Yeah!

rows.label: qst202901_0630
rows.name:
D'you think I can be as pretty as Tsuki
if I work hard enough?

rows.label: qst202901_0640
rows.name:
Sure! 'Y'all gotta work hard to talk
"cool" like li'l old Tsuki!'

rows.label: qst202901_0650
rows.name: Zeke! That's not very...

rows.label: qst202901_0660
rows.name:
Wow!
Thanks, pretty lady Tsuki!

rows.label: qst202901_0670
rows.name:
Next time we meet, I'm gonna
be super pretty too!

rows.label: qst202901_0680
rows.name: Bye-bye!

rows.label: qst202901_0690
rows.name:
Bye, hon!
You work hard now!

rows.label: qst202901_0700
rows.name: That is one happy customer.

rows.label: qst202901_0710
rows.name:
Yeah, Tsuki, I never knew you
were so good with kids!

rows.label: qst202901_0720
rows.name:
Oh, I'm nothin' special.
That was just a fluke, is all.

rows.label: qst202901_0730
rows.name:
And as for you, Zeke...!
I don't like your cheek!

rows.label: qst202901_0740
rows.name: Hahaha!

rows.label: qst202901_0750
rows.name:
Just to get back at you for mocking
my cool way of talking.

rows.label: qst202901_0760
rows.name: What are we gonna do with you...?

rows.label: qst202901_0770
rows.name:
I must say, I'm looking forward to the
next time we run into that young lady.

rows.label: qst202901_0780
rows.name:
And how!
I just hope she doesn't push herself TOO hard...
